title: Travalo Travel Spray By Travalo - Mini Travel Refillable Spray with Cap Refills From Any Fragrance Bottle (Hot Pink) .135 Oz
description: We all wish we could take our favorite colognes and perfumes wherever we go, but decanting is just too messy. Now Travalo, a company based in the U.K. offers smaller travel-size flacons that are refillable. This is the perfect size for a pocket, for airport travel or a handbag. This great item is available in a wide range of colors and hold up to 50 sprays of your favorite scent. So now you are scent to go...

title: Travalo (iPump5 new! Zero Leaks!) (Silver)
description: Wish you had an easier way to carry your favorite scent wherever you go? Now you do! The Travalo Classic Perfume Atomizer replaces the big, heavy, and potentially dangerous glass perfume or aftershave bottle in your bag, and is made with a sturdy aluminum exterior with an unbreakable fragrance reservoir to guarantee reliable pumps and travel convenience.The Classic Perfume Atomizer refills in seconds, holds at least a week's worth (50-60 sprays) of fragrance and is small enough to carry in a purse or pocket.Thanks to Travalo's Genie-S technology, the Atomizer fills directly from any normal atomizer fragrance bottle, won't leak in your bag, and is easy to fill without awkward funnels and messy spills. Take your own fragrance with you every time. Take Travalo. *perfectly rounded with no corners or edges and slips into a pocket easily *lightweight *full sized spray head *no leaking *quick to fill *fills directly from any normal atomizer fragrance bottle *works with most bottles with a removable nozzle *aircraft approved - safe in hand luggage *98% of Travalo is recyclable

title: real Techniques Powder Brush
description: Designed with pro makeup artist Samantha Chapman, Real Techniques brushes combine high-tech materials with innovative design to make creating a pixel-perfect look easier than ever: Taklon bristles are ultra plush and smoother than the hair you'll find in other brushes. Since taklon is synthetic, it's 100% cruelty-free. The soft fibers help create a flawless, high-definition finish in any type of light, from sunlight to harsh indoor lighting. The color-coded system corresponds to the key steps of makeup application so you can create a flawless base (copper), enhanced eyes (purple), and the perfect finish like a pro (pink). Each brush head is hand-cut to the perfect shape, allowing for precise application from dense coverage to a soft, delicate finish. The collection is suitable for a wide range of products and every makeup need – from powders, creams, and liquids to mineral makeup, highlighter, and shimmer. Brush names on the handles make for easy reference when creating your favorite look.
